data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the heart of Sanger! The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, kitchen, and dining areas, creating an ideal setting for entertaining friends and family. Equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, a convenient breakfast bar and a dinning space, the kitchen is truly the heart of this home. Retreat to the comfort of the master suite, that includes a private bathroom and provides a tranquil escape from the day's demands. The backyard is large in size, and has a great covered patio that is perfect for summer barbecues or simply unwinding after a long day.

Nestled in a sought-after Sanger neighborhood, this home is conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping. Enjoy the benefits of a quiet community while still having easy access to local amenities.Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or an investor, this property presents an excellent opportunity.

Contact your realtor today for a private showing!
